Use the following command to load MySQL database for PHT:
$ mysql -u user -p < DDL.sql

This step must be performed before runnig the server - client codes.

To insert a fictitious set of data stored in file pht.data, use the following syntax:

mysql>source /absolute_path/to_file/file.name; /* non usare apici */

Per alterare una colonna in una tabella:
alter table ScienceGoals modify scienceGoalsID int not null auto_increment;
